detail.title: BUCK
detail.description: BUCK is creative payment mobile application project of Westpac, it provides a the fast, easy, and free way to pay friends and get money from them.
detail.responsibility: I participated in this project for building the website and dashboard by using React, Gatsby.js and Material UI.
detail.tech: React, Typescript, Jest, Gatsby.js, Material UI, CircleCI, EDM
